pageContext.claim: “Police Chief, and most of the police in Rochester, N.Y., have resigned. The Democrat Mayor and, of courses, Governor Cuomo, have no idea what to do. New York State is a mess - No Money, High Taxes & Crime, Everyone Fleeing. November 3rd. We can fix it!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump is missing the context here. The Rochester police chief and other high-ranking officials resigned amid controversy over the death of a man in police custody.
